item.title: CVE-2024-32560|2024-04-18T10:05:16.451Z -- Sharabindu -- QR Code Composer
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in Sharabindu QR Code Composer allows Stored XSS.This issue affects QR Code Composer: from n/a through 2.0.3.
